{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM06_ST4_090.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x25,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "H-Huh...? We're in the herb garden behind the workshop!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I wonder why... I thought we'd be way farther away..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "After engaging in that battle, I knew it would be difficult to travel all the way back."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "So, I connected the exit here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "So that's why...<CR>Actually, I'm exhausted, so I'm glad..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "There wasn't any other way to save Nio, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "You have not made a single wrong decision. He was broken to begin with."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "At least, that's my opinion,<CR>but you don't seem convinced."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Yeah... He was just fulfilling the desire of a past alchemist."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "He was just faithfully doing his duty, and we destroyed him."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "It's like we erased the desire of his creator, and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x91,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "The disasters of the past are long gone. The threat he would rescue us from no longer exists."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x92,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Though, we may be standing on the precipice of the end of human history..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x92,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "However, it's still too early for us to need to be in his care."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x93,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "There is more than one solution, and I am searching for a different path."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "A different path...!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Yes, and the best thing you can do for him would be to find your own, more proper, solution."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I don't think I can find a clear solution right away, but I'll keep an eye out for what I can do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Hey you two, you seem to be having a serious conversation."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "So...what are you talking about?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "...Hmhm. See? Now you have your sister with you. Could this not be your answer?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "You're right. No matter what might've happened, I still would've taken Nio back."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "That's good. Never regret what you've done..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Because you are an alchemist."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "...Yes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "You probably have a lot to contemplate and do, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "For today, rest well. It'll be nice to spend some time together, just you sisters."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "After that, if you still have anything left to do, you can start doing it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Keith..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Well, I'll be going now. Farewell."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Keith...umm...thank you so much for everything."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "That man seemed like a nice person.<CR>Do you know him?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Yup. He's kinda like my synthesis teacher. But yeah..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "I think Mr. Keith is a nice person, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "But I feel like he's gone through a really sad experience..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...I see. I guess it really was a serious conversation..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, well, we should go home. To the workshop! Pana is waiting for us, too!"
        }
    ]
}